    "title": "Add approval gate and bot management UI",
    "body": "<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_BEGIN -->\n## Summary\n- Add a traffic approval gate before the app opens, backed by configured approval codes.\n- Add constrained bot management with app-owned presets for prompts/settings/plugins and user-only API key, Thinking, and Search controls.\n- Restore mobile phone OTP sign-in and add contact sync from supported browsers into leads.\n- Include generated JavaScript companion files emitted by the repo's TypeScript build.\n- Harden approval storage access so unavailable browser storage cannot crash the app.\n- Merge latest `main` and resolve the simple add/add conflicts in `src/lib/access.ts` and `src/lib/access.js` by keeping the guarded storage implementation.\n\n## Verification\n- `npm run build`\n<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_END -->\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents/bc-89dfb845-ff67-4023-9b12-8382a9d54534\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" width=\"114\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-89dfb845-ff67-4023-9b12-8382a9d54534\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" width=\"131\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;</div>\n\n",
